pairing. What would life be like without pairs? How miserable would life be with couples being shunned and viewed as outsiders? God gave a beautiful plan. He brought women together with men to have children and build a great society. Get Married!

Marriage is a calling in marriage from God. It is not a onetime decision but a lifelong commitment where you work on loving and supporting your spouse, committing to staying together, and overcoming the world’s challenges together.

Here are why you should consider pairing yourself up.

A chance of having children

Without children, humanity would all be wiped off the earth since without the younger generation coming up, the world would collapse. A baby is a blessing from God, and it is wise that more human beings have them.

Having a child also provides companionship for you and your spouse. You can also enjoy seeing others grow and have children of your own.

Gives you companionship

You don’t want to grow old alone now, do you? Then there is a reason you should get married. With no spouse to stand with you through struggles, helping you to live life in a more comfortable way you’ll become lonely. Loneliness can lead to health complications such as mental illnesses and physical incapacitation. That’s no way of living If you ask me (and you asked, didn’t you?)

So get married and share your life with somebody. You’ll never regret finding your better half.
